txx=txx+"~spec.consts:~`y` = true / `n` = false ~`g` = graph.window~`t` = textwindow~`s` = shapes~`a` = array~`c` = controls~`f` = file~`p` = prog.~`x` = text~\\ = LD xtension~

txx=txx+"!n> /fnm/ /p1/ /p2/ ... /pn/ | call func w args 1..n 

